{"tid":1125844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘破毒品飯堂 警擒14男女","createTime":"2019-04-26T03:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T03:34:48.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"caf2f8cb928317fde235e8bc68d79082204dbf04","tid":1125844,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T03:34:48.000Z","msg":"觀塘警區特別職務隊人員根據線報及經深入調查後，昨日（25日）下午約6時進行反毒品行動，突擊搜查康寧道32至38號一單位，檢獲市值約1.5萬元的毒品，拘捕14人。<br />\n<br />\n人員在單位內檢獲約20克懷疑「冰」毒、約4克懷疑可卡因及現金約4000元。一名48姓吳本地男子涉嫌販毒、經營煙窟及藏毒被捕。<br />\n<br />\n單位內另外11名本地男子及2名本地女子，年齡介乎36至70歲，則涉嫌吸食毒品被捕。當中一名43歲男子身上有小量懷疑「冰」毒及一名62歲女子有針筒，亦分別涉嫌藏毒及藏有工具可作吸食毒品用途被捕。<br />\n<br />\n所有被捕人士現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190426/_2019042609390054417.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190426%2F_2019042609390054417.jpg&h=37697ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/987532-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E7%A0%B4%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E9%A3%AF%E5%A0%82+%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%9214%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F987532-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25A0%2582%2B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2593%259214%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=e99feec1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F987532-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25A0%2582%2B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2593%259214%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3&h=a0a458b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/987532-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E7%A0%B4%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E9%A3%AF%E5%A0%82+%E8%AD%A6%E6%93%9214%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3</a>"}]}